<li><a href="#org2ea268b">45.4. There is more buying pressure than selling pressure, so the supply and demand factor is +10%.</a></li>
<li><a href="#org4b35437">45.5. The reference price is $3.33.</a></li>
<li><a href="#orgc05df6b">45.6. The adjusted reference price is $3.66.</a></li>
<li><a href="#orga59dcc3">45.7. The adjusted reference price is within the allowed range.</a></li>
<li><a href="#orgcd0abb2">45.8. The opening or closing price is set at $3.66.</a></li>
