<td class="org-left">Securities trading</td>
<td class="org-left">N/A</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">Outcome</td>
<td class="org-left">Used to select the best available price for the investor</td>
<td class="org-left">N/A</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">Terminology</td>
<td class="org-left">Referred to as "competitive quotes" or "competitive bids"</td>
<td class="org-left">N/A</td>
</tr>
