<h2 id="org4722a05"><span class="section-number-2">20.</span> Multi-Day event for clearly erroneous trades.</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-20">
<table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides">


<colgroup>
<col  class="org-left" />

<col  class="org-left" />
</colgroup>
