<div id="outline-container-org4c021fc" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org4c021fc"><span class="section-number-2">26.</span> size</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-26">
<p>
0.0001-0.0999: 10,000 shares
0.10-0.1999: 5,000 shares
0.20-0.5099: 2,500 shares
0.51-0.9999: 1,000 shares
1.00-174.99: 100 shares
175.00+: 1 share
</p>

<p>
10000 * .0001 / 0.0001  1/10000
5000  * 0.1   / 0.1     1/10
2500  * 0.2   / 0.2     1/5
1000  * 0.5   / 0.5     1/2
100   * 1     / 1       1
1
</p>
</div>
