<div id="outline-container-orgbd45b66" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgbd45b66"><span class="section-number-3">35.1.</span> Circuit Breaker Rules</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-35-1">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orge801038" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orge801038"><span class="section-number-4">35.1.1.</span> Table summarizing the Designated Percentage requirements for different types of stocks and exchanges:</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-35-1-1">
